videos.headline: Milton connects with Smith for Knights' TD
videos.description: McKenzie Milton finds Tre'Quan Smith in the end zone for a 34-yard touchdown to extend the UCF's lead.

tracking.trackingName: Com_NCF_One Play (Milton connects with Smith for Knights' TD)

videos.headline: Killins strikes again with 19-yard TD catch
videos.description: UCF's McKenzie Milton passes it to Adrian Killins Jr. who catches it and takes it to the house to further the Knight's lead.

videos.headline: UCF scores on nice TD pass from Milton
videos.description: McKenzie Milton airs it out and finds Tre'Quan Smith in the end zone for a 25-yard touchdown to add to the Knight's lead.
